<img class="alignright" src="http://www.insulationproducts.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/ip63es.jpg" alt="Very flexible / conforms to irregular shapes" />

&nbsp;

<strong>Roundit® 2000</strong> <strong>Sleeving: <a href="http://www.insulationproducts.com/non-shrink-tubing/sleeving/roundit-2000-sleeving/">IP63ES</a>                                                                                                                                                           </strong>

Roundit® is a tough, lightweight, self-wrapping sleeving designed to allow for quick and easy application and removal. Made from a woven blend of polyester monofilaments and multifilaments in a flat weave construction gives Roundit® a rugged yet smooth appearance.

&nbsp;

