<img class="alignright" src="http://www.insulationproducts.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/ip64fs-1.jpg" alt="For very high temperature applications" />

&nbsp;

<strong>Fiberglass Sleeving: <a href="http://www.insulationproducts.com/non-shrink-tubing/sleeving/fiberglass-sleeving/">IP64FS / IPC65VC / IP66AC / IP67SC</a></strong>

For very high temperature applications. Fiberglass sleeving is designed for heat resistance along with a variety of coatings to meet specific thermal and dielectric requirements.<strong> </strong>

